'''丹尼爾·威廉·約翰·艾格斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Daniel William John Ings'''}}，{{bd|1992年|7月23日|catidx=Ings, Danny}}），是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]足球運動員，司職[[前鋒|前鋒]]。現效力於[[英超|英超]]球隊[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]。他同時亦是英格蘭代表隊成員。

艾格斯在{{Fc|修咸頓}}展開其足球生涯，但在學童時期已被放棄。他其後加入般尼茅夫的精英中心，經過訓練後於2008年夏天簽署兩年的學徒合約。他在2009年10月首次獲得職業賽事上陣機會。2010年5月首次簽職業合約，並於同年9月延長合約期，而在同月他外借加盟[[英格蘭足球議會南部聯賽|英議南]]的球隊{{FC|多爾切斯特}}，為期兩個月。他於2011年2月首次為般尼茅夫攻入首個職業賽入球。2011年8月，他加盟[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[般尼|般尼]]，簽約4年。

球場外的艾格斯以熱心慈善為名<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/news/11252635.Burnley_striker_Danny_shows_his_car_Ing_side/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-04-18 |archive-date=2018-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180626164400/http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/news/11252635.Burnley_striker_Danny_shows_his_car_Ing_side/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年11月，他的「丹尼·艾格斯傷健人士體育項目」正式啟動並注資其中，為身體殘障及學習障礙的兒童提供足球訓練機會。他進行這個項目的原因是受到一名年輕的殘疾般尼球迷所啟發<ref>http://www.thefa.com/news/england/under-21/2014/nov/danny-ings-disabled-sport-project-launch-251114</ref>。

==球會生涯==
===般尼茅夫===
艾格斯出生於近[[南安普頓|南安普頓]]的海德<ref name="New intake for coach Joe">{{cite news | url = http://www.bournemouthecho.co.uk/sport/2268488.new_intake_for_coach_joe/ | publisher = ''Daily Echo'' | first = Ian | last = Wadley | title = New intake for coach Joe | date = 14 May 2008 | accessdate = 16 October 2009 | archive-date = 2018-09-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180920084406/https://www.bournemouthecho.co.uk/sport/2268488.New_intake_for_coach_Joe/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他在{{FC|修咸頓}}展開其足球生涯，但在學童時期已被放棄<ref name="Cherries: Boss Lee offers Ings brand new contract">{{cite news | url = http://www.bournemouthecho.co.uk/sport/9141445.Cherries__Boss_Lee_offers_Ings_brand_new_contract/ | publisher = ''Daily Echo'' | first = Neil | last = Perrett | title = Cherries: Boss Lee offers Ings brand new contract | date = 15 July 2011 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | archive-date = 2018-07-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180713014138/http://www.bournemouthecho.co.uk/sport/9141445.Cherries__Boss_Lee_offers_Ings_brand_new_contract/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他其後加入般尼茅夫的精英中心，經過訓練後於2008年夏天簽署兩年的學徒合約。<ref name="New intake for coach Joe"/>他在之前亦有代表預備隊上陣的經驗<ref name="New intake for coach Joe"/>。2009年10月6日他首次為般尼茅夫踢職業賽，在[[英格蘭足總錦標|英格蘭足總錦標]]作客以1:2不敵{{FC|諾咸頓}}的賽事中下半場後備入替積臣·泰杜爾<ref name="Northampton 2 - 1 Bournemouth">{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8284875.stm | publisher = BBC Sport | title = Northampton 2 – 1 Bournemouth | date = 6 October 2009 | accessdate = 16 October 2009 | archive-date = 2022-02-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220211102003/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8284875.stm }}</ref>。他在青年軍的第二季卻因腹部的長期受傷而蒙上陰影，他的上陣時間受限<ref name="Cherries: Hot-shot Ings can only get better">{{cite news | url = http://www.bournemouthecho.co.uk/sport/8828804.Cherries__Hot_shot_Ings_can_only_get_better/ | publisher = ''Daily Echo'' | first = Ian | last = Wadley | title = Cherries: Hot-shot Ings can only get better | date = 3 February 2011 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | archive-date = 2018-09-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180901215758/http://www.bournemouthecho.co.uk/sport/8828804.Cherries__Hot_shot_Ings_can_only_get_better/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他一直留效青年軍直至2010年夏天，當時他簽署為期三個月的短期合約<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.bournemouthecho.co.uk/sport/8711429.Cherries__Howe_has_high_hopes_for_star_Ings/?action=complain&cid=8964719 | publisher = ''Daily Echo'' | first = Ian | last = Wadley | title = Cherries: Howe has high hopes for star Ings | date = 1 December 2010 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | archive-date = 2018-08-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180810144143/http://www.bournemouthecho.co.uk/sport/8711429.Cherries__Howe_has_high_hopes_for_star_Ings/?action=complain&cid=8964719 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在2010年9月他獲球隊續約至季尾<ref name="Cherries: Boss Lee offers Ings brand new contract"/>。

2010年9月，他外借加盟英議南球隊{{FC|多爾切斯特}}，為期一個月<ref name="Ings and out for Magpies">{{cite news | url = http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/news/2010/september/11-1.shtml | publisher = ''Dorchester Town'' | first = Adan | last = Summers | title = Ings and out for Magpies | date = 11 September 2010 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130420101900/http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/news/2010/september/11-1.shtml | archivedate = 2013年4月20日 }}</ref>。2010年9月11日首次為新球會上陣，主場迎戰[[艾贝斯费特联足球俱乐部|艾貝斯費特]]，他雖一度為球隊追平，但仍以1:2落敗<ref name="Ebbing away">{{cite news | url = http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/season/201011/reports/ebbsfleet-h-bsbs.shtml | publisher = ''Dorchester Town'' | first = Ky | last = Capel | title = Ebbing away | date = 11 September 2010 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130420043611/http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/season/201011/reports/ebbsfleet-h-bsbs.shtml | archivedate = 2013年4月20日 }}</ref>。他第二個入球是在9月24日的[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]對[[曼斯菲尔德城足球俱乐部|曼斯菲尔德城]]射入[[十二碼|十二碼]]，助球隊贏4:1<ref name="Mangoes crushed by Magpies">{{cite news | url = http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/season/201011/reports/mangotsfield-a-fac.shtml | publisher = ''Dorchester Town'' | title = Mangoes crushed by Magpies | date = 25 September 2010 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130420094120/http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/season/201011/reports/mangotsfield-a-fac.shtml | archivedate = 2013年4月20日 }}</ref>。10月6日，他的租約延長一個月<ref name="Loanee Danny extends Magpies stay">{{cite news | url = http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/news/2010/october/06-1.shtml | publisher = ''Dorchester Town'' | first = Ky | last = Capel | title = Loanee Danny extends Magpies stay | date = 6 October 2010 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130420024801/http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/news/2010/october/06-1.shtml | archivedate = 2013年4月20日 }}</ref>。他在對[[哈雲特|哈雲特]]的足總盃中再為球隊入球，但仍以1:4落敗並出局<ref name="Magpies' cup dream is over">{{cite news | url = http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/season/201011/reports/havant-a-fac.shtml | publisher = ''Dorchester Town'' | first = Ky | last = Capel | title = Magpies' cup dream is over | date = 9 October 2010 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130420075356/http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/season/201011/reports/havant-a-fac.shtml | archivedate = 2013年4月20日 }}</ref>。10月16日，他以後備身份為球隊攻入第二個聯賽入球，助球隊以2:0贏[[雷威斯足球會|雷威斯]]<ref name="Loan duo strike for Magpies">{{cite news | url = http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/season/201011/reports/lewes-a-bsbs.shtml | publisher = ''Dorchester Town'' | first = Ky | last = Capel | title = Loan duo strike for Magpies | date = 16 October 2010 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130420032857/http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/season/201011/reports/lewes-a-bsbs.shtml | archivedate = 2013年4月20日 }}</ref>。他的第五個入球是作客對[[斯坦斯鎮足球會|斯坦斯鎮]]取得的，為球隊先開紀錄並以2:1取勝<ref name="Moss earns treble for Magpies">{{cite news | url = http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/season/201011/reports/staines-a-bsbs.shtml | publisher = ''Dorchester Town'' | first = Ky | last = Capel | title = Moss earns treble for Magpies | date = 30 October 2010 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130420005635/http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/season/201011/reports/staines-a-bsbs.shtml | archivedate = 2013年4月20日 }}</ref>。11月在主場對[[梅頓赫德聯足球會|梅頓赫德聯]]雖取得入球，但仍以1:2落敗，6場不敗紀錄終止<ref name="Magpies' run ended">{{cite news | url = http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/season/201011/reports/maidenhead-h-bsbs.shtml | publisher = ''Dorchester Town'' | first = Ky | last = Capel | title = Magpies' run ended | date = 9 November 2010 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130420004016/http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/season/201011/reports/maidenhead-h-bsbs.shtml | archivedate = 2013年4月20日 }}</ref> 。2010年11月12日，他的外借期再延長一個月.<ref name="Danny boy delight for Magpies">{{cite news | url = http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/news/2010/november/12-1.shtml | publisher = ''Dorchester Town'' | first = Ky | last = Capel | title = Danny boy delight for Magpies | date = 12 November 2010 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130420002514/http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/news/2010/november/12-1.shtml | archivedate = 2013年4月20日 }}</ref>。足總錦標對韋斯頓的賽事為球隊攻入第二球，助球隊贏3:1並成功出線<ref name="Away-day joy earns £4,000 for Magpies">{{cite news | url = http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/season/201011/reports/weston-a-fat.shtml | publisher = ''Dorchester Town'' | first = Ky | last = Capel | title = Away-day joy earns £4,000 for Magpies | date = 20 November 2010 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130422042120/http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/season/201011/reports/weston-a-fat.shtml | archivedate = 2013年4月22日 }}</ref>。11月23日，因般尼茅夫的傷患問題嚴重，會方終止外借合約並召回他入隊<ref name="Danny departs Magpies">{{cite news | url = http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/news/2010/november/23-1.shtml | publisher = ''Dorchester Town'' | first = Ky | last = Capel | title = Danny departs Magpies | date = 23 November 2010 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130420090601/http://www.dorchestertownfc.co.uk/news/2010/november/23-1.shtml | archivedate = 2013年4月20日 }}</ref>。

11月30日，他與球隊續約至2012年<ref name="Cherries: Ings signs contract extension">{{cite news | url = http://www.bournemouthecho.co.uk/sport/8711361.Cherries__Ings_signs_contract_extension/ | publisher = ''Daily Echo'' | first = Neil | last = Perrett | title = Cherries: Ings signs contract extension | date = 30 November 2010 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | archive-date = 2018-08-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180810144034/http://www.bournemouthecho.co.uk/sport/8711361.Cherries__Ings_signs_contract_extension/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2010年12月28日首次為般尼茅夫在[[英甲|英甲]]正選上陣，卻在作客以0:2不敵[[米尔顿凯恩斯足球俱乐部|米尔顿凯恩斯]]，但他卻在上半場被[[史提夫·費查|史提夫·費查]]入替<ref name="MK Dons 2 - 0 Bournemouth">{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/9304980.stm | publisher = BBC Sport | title = MK Dons 2 – 0 Bournemouth | date = 28 December 2010 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 }}</ref>。他之後躋身球隊的正選陣容，並在2011年2月1日對{{FC|史雲頓}}的賽事中為球隊攻入首個職業賽入球，助球隊3:2擊敗對手<ref name="Bournemouth 3 - 2 Swindon">{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/9377131.stm | publisher = BBC Sport | title = Bournemouth 3 – 2 Swindon | date = 1 February 2011 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | archive-date = 2021-11-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211110070545/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/9377131.stm }}</ref>。憑藉出色的表現，他獲會方續約至2013年<ref name="Cherries: Boss Lee offers Ings brand new contract"/>。2011年2月26日，他在對{{fc|杜根咸}}的聯賽中為球隊以頭槌扳平，後來更以2:1反勝<ref name="Dag & Red 1 - 2 Bournemouth">{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/9401900.stm | publisher = BBC Sport | title = Dag & Red 1 – 2 Bournemouth | date = 26 February 2011 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 }}</ref>。4月1日以3:3賽和{{fc|彼德堡}}的聯賽中再下一城<ref name="Peterborough 3 - 3 Bournemouth">{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/9436462.stm | publisher = BBC Sport | title = Peterborough 3 – 3 Bournemouth | date = 1 April 2011 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 }}</ref>。4月他可謂大豐收，在3場賽事攻入4球。他在對{{fc|燦美爾}}的賽事以[[倒掛|倒掛]]在賽事末段追和，但仍被反絕殺1:2落敗<ref name="Bournemouth 1 - 2 Tranmere">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/12945348 | publisher = BBC Sport | title = Bournemouth 1 – 2 Tranmere | date = 9 April 2011 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | archive-date = 2015-10-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151006142039/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/12945348 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。作客2:0擊敗{{fc|諾士郡}}一戰中亦取得入球<ref name="Notts County 0 - 2 Bournemouth">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13022988 | publisher = BBC Sport | title = Notts County 0 – 2 Bournemouth | date = 16 April 2011 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | archive-date = 2014-10-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141012002853/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13022988 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。對{{fc|伊奧維}}一戰中首次[[梅開二度|梅開二度]]，包括一個十二碼，但只能2:2賽和對手<ref name="Yeovil 2 - 2 Bournemouth">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13102925 | publisher = BBC Sport | title = Yeovil 2 – 2 Bournemouth | date = 23 April 2011 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | archive-date = 2015-10-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151005162255/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13102925 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在球季的謝幕戰，他為般尼茅夫取得最後一個入球，是在對[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈德斯菲尔德]]的升班附加賽四強取得的，但球隊終在[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]中落敗<ref name="Huddersfield 3 - 3 Bournemouth">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13356811 | publisher = BBC Sport | title = Huddersfield 3 – 3 Bournemouth | date = 18 May 2011 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | archive-date = 2014-02-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140203142240/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13356811 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2011年夏天，有報導指[[些路迪|些路迪]]、{{fc|利物浦}}和{{fc|紐卡素}}均有意羅致他<ref name="Cherries: Boss Lee offers Ings brand new contract"/>，而[[英超|英超]]球隊{{fc|富咸}}出價40萬鎊更遭到會方婉拒<ref name="Cherries: Boss Lee offers Ings brand new contract"/>。2011年7月，他第五度與球會續約，為期一年，他更因此成為球隊的頂薪一族<ref name="Cherries: Boss Lee offers Ings brand new contract"/>。在季前他仍留在球隊，而作客不敵{{fc|查爾頓}}0:3一戰中正選上陣，這場賽事是他對般尼茅夫的最後一戰<ref name="Charlton 3 - 0 Bournemouth">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/14351895 | publisher = BBC Sport | title = Charlton 3 – 0 Bournemouth | date = 6 August 2011 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | archive-date = 2015-10-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151001001708/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/14351895 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

===般尼===
[[File:Chelsea_1_Burnley_1_(16427538130)_(2).jpg|thumb]]的[[蘇馬|蘇馬]]爭持]]
2011年8月15日，他正式加盟[[英冠|英冠]]的{{fc|般尼}}，官方未有公布轉會費，但外界估計為100萬鎊，合約為期四年<ref name="Burnley sign Bournemouth striker Danny Ings">{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/9564859.stm | publisher = BBC Sport | title = Burnley sign Bournemouth striker Danny Ings  | date = 15 August 2011 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 }}</ref>。他與早八個月來投的前般尼茅夫領隊艾迪·賀維重聚。2012年2月14日擊敗{{fc|班士利}}一戰中首次上陣，後備入替[[查理·柯士甸|查理·柯士甸]]<ref name="Burnley 2-0 Barnsley">{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/9564859.stm | publisher = BBC Sport | title = Burnley 2–0 Barnsley | date = 14 February 2012 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 }}</ref>。2012年3月10日首次正選上陣，該仗在主場1:1賽和{{fc|水晶宮}}<ref name="Burnley 1-1 Crystal Palace">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17243698 | publisher = BBC Sport | title = Burnley 1–1 Crystal Palace | date = 10 March 2012 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | archive-date = 2014-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140304075244/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17243698 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。3 月31日在作客5:1大勝{{fc|樸茨茅夫}}中取得首個入球<ref name="Portsmouth 1-5 Burnley">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17496929 | publisher = BBC Sport | title = Portsmouth 1–5 Burnley | date = 31 March 2012 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | archive-date = 2012-04-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120402010117/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17496929 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他在緊接的一場再取得入球，對{{fc|伯明翰}}一戰為球隊追和，但最終仍以1:3落敗<ref name="Burnley 1-3 Birmingham">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17520522 | publisher = BBC Sport | title = Burnley 1–3 Birmingham | date = 3 April 2012 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | archive-date = 2012-04-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120404002554/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17520522 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。賽季最後一戰他為球隊攻入第三球，1:1戰和{{fc|布里斯托城}}中以30碼遠射得手.<ref name="Burnley 1-1 Bristol City">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17795497 | publisher = BBC Sport | title = Burnley 1–1 Bristol City | date = 28 April 2012 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | archive-date = 2012-06-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120626120616/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17795497 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2012/13球季，在球隊將[[積·洛迪古斯|積·洛迪古斯]]賣給{{fc|修咸頓}}後，他成為球隊的首選前鋒。對{{fc|艾川查姆}}及{{fc|貝利}}的季前賽先後取得入球<ref name="PHOTOS: Altrincham 1, Burnley 4 ">{{cite news | url = http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/9208461.Howe_blow_as_Ings_needs_knee_surgery/ | publisher = ''Burnley Express'' | first = Dan | last = Black | title = PHOTOS: Altrincham 1, Burnley 4 | date = 23 July 2012 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | archive-date = 2018-10-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181003101112/https://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/9208461.Howe_blow_as_Ings_needs_knee_surgery/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="BURY 0 BURNLEY 1">{{cite news | url = http://www.burnleyfootballclub.com/page/LatestHeadlines/0,,10413~2859646,00.html | publisher = ''Burnley F.C.'' | title = BURY 0 BURNLEY 1 | date = 14 August 2012 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120827083518/http://www.burnleyfootballclub.com/page/LatestHeadlines/0%2C%2C10413~2859646%2C00.html | archivedate = 2012年8月27日 }}</ref>在最後一場季前賽以1:3不敵{{fc|羅奇代爾}}一戰遭到嚴重的腿傷。他在上季在另一隻腳已曾嘗過斷腿骨而需要接受手術，這次他亦要休戰半年<ref name="Burnley's Danny Ings faces up six months out with knee injury">{{cite news | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19242581 | publisher = BBC Sport | title = Burnley's Danny Ings faces up six months out with knee injury | date = 13 August 2012 | accessdate = 14 September 2012 | archive-date = 2015-08-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150802073004/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19242581 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2013/14球季他復出後延續其季前賽的出色表現，在球隊開季的三場聯賽攻入兩球之餘，更為在[[英聯盃|英聯盃]]對{{fc|約克城}}取得入球.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23499462 |title=Burnley easily negotiated their way past League Two York City to reach the Capital One Cup second round. |accessdate=2015-04-18 |archive-date=2013-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131220001340/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23499462 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2014年3月，艾格斯擊敗{{fc|列斯聯}}射手[[麥哥馬克|麥哥馬克]]和{{fc|李斯特城}}中場[[丹尼尔·德林克沃特|德林克沃特]]而贏得英冠最佳球員獎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.football-league.co.uk/flawards/news/20140316/football-league-awards-2014-winners_2293338_3716321 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321005206/http://www.football-league.co.uk/flawards/news/20140316/football-league-awards-2014-winners_2293338_3716321 |archivedate=2014-03-21 }}</ref>。他憑藉全季的穩定出色表現，助球隊提早升班，為般尼事隔四年重返英超。

2014年11月22日，他在2:1擊敗{{fc|史篤城}}一戰中在兩分鐘內連入兩球，助球隊贏得本季的首場作客勝仗<ref>{{cite news|last1=Emons|first1=Michael|title=Stoke 1–2 Burnley|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30065845|accessdate=23 November 2014|work=BBC Sport|date=22 November 2014|archive-date=2015-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150823033845/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30065845|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12月13日以1:0擊敗{{fc|修咸頓}}一戰，是他為般尼上陣的第一百場賽事<ref>{{cite news|last1=Sanghera|first1=Mandeep|title=Burnley 1-0 Southampton|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30357668|accessdate=11 January 2015|work=BBC Sport|date=13 December 2014|archive-date=2016-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121092154/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30357668|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年1月10日，他對[[QPR|QPR]]的[[護級|護級]]大戰中攻入致勝一球，助球隊2:1擊敗對手並暫時逃出[[降班|降班]]區<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bevan|first1=Chris|title=Burnley 2-1 QPR|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30663821|accessdate=11 January 2015|work=BBC Sport|date=10 January 2015|archive-date=2015-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724202808/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30663821|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2月12日作客對曼聯時，艾格斯一度在12分鐘替般尼追和，但球隊仍只能以1:3落敗。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/31124671 |title=Substitute Chris Smalling scored twice to help Manchester United overcome battling Burnley and climb up to third in the Premier League table. |accessdate=2015-04-18 |archive-date=2015-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150306085339/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/31124671 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===利物浦===
2015年6月8日，利物浦宣佈同意簽下艾格斯，季後他與般尼的合約到期後加盟球隊。2015年7月9日，艾格斯正式加盟利物浦。不過由於艾格斯未滿24歲，因此利物浦需要向般尼支付培養費，但雙方未能就金額達成共識，將由審裁處作出決定。在2016年4月28日，職業足球賠償委員會裁決利物浦需要向般尼支付650萬英鎊的初始培養費，此外包含了與球員表現相掛勾的150萬英鎊的附加條款。

===南安普頓===
經過一季的外借，2019年7月1日，艾格斯正式轉會至南安普頓。<ref>{{cite web |title=Danny Ings: Southampton sign Liverpool striker for £20m |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/48831514 |website=BBC Sport |access-date=2 July 2019 |archive-date=2021-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524171930/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/48831514 }}</ref>

==國家隊==
2013年10月3日，艾格斯首次入選[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]名單，備戰[[聖馬力諾21歲以下國家足球隊|聖馬力諾U21]]及[[立陶宛21歲以下國家足球隊|立陶宛U21]]兩場[[2015年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2015年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]外圍賽。於10月10日[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]作客對[[聖馬力諾21歲以下國家足球隊|聖馬力諾U21]]的賽事，艾格斯於下半場21分鐘上場，成為其首場國際賽<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2013/oct/10/san-marino-england-euro-2015-qualifier |title=England Under-21s thrash San Marino thanks to Harry Kane's hat-trick |publisher=''The Guardian'' |date=2013-10-10 |accessdate=2013-11-09 |archive-date=2020-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106045839/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2013/oct/10/san-marino-england-euro-2015-qualifier |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年9月5日，睽違已久再次入選[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭足球代表隊]]名單，[[2020–21年歐洲國家聯賽|歐洲國家聯賽]]以1比0擊敗[[冰島國家足球隊|冰島]]的比賽中第68分鐘替補上場。

2020年10月8日，英斯在[[溫布利球場|溫布利球場]]對陣[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯]]的友誼賽，踢進了自己的第一個國際進球，以頭球方式進球幫助英格蘭隊3-0獲得勝利。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/54366319 |title="England 3–0 Wales" |accessdate=2020-10-17 |archive-date=2020-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016043444/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/54366319 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

